TEXT.S: = Cihak = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Sowfungsyang ka alang Cihak. 995 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 2,905 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 13% niqan 379 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 87% niqan 2,526 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis 9%, Truku 1%, Tayal 1%, Bunun 1%.
